 <fr:p>Fixing <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x:A]]></fr:tex>, we must construct an identification from <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H  \mathopen {}\left \lparen f x\right \rparen \mathclose {} ]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {act}_{f}  \mathopen {}\left \lparen H x\right \rparen \mathclose {} ]]></fr:tex>. By the naturality (<fr:ref
addr="erct-001V"
href="erct-001V.xml"
taxon="Lemma" />) of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H]]></fr:tex> at the identification <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H x\colon  f x = x]]></fr:tex>, we have an identification <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H  \mathopen {}\left \lparen f x\right \rparen \mathclose {}  \cdot  \mathsf {act}_{1_{A}}  \mathopen {}\left \lparen H x\right \rparen \mathclose {}  = \mathsf {act}_{f}  \mathopen {}\left \lparen H x\right \rparen \mathclose {} \cdot  H x]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 <fr:p>Simplifying, we have <fr:tex
