display="inline"><![CDATA[H x]]></fr:tex> on either side, we therefore have the desired identification <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H  \mathopen {}\left \lparen f x\right \rparen \mathclose {}  = \mathsf {act}_{f}  \mathopen {}\left \lparen H x\right \rparen \mathclose {} ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
